Class KijiTableInputFormat

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.InputFormat<EntityId,KijiRowData>
      org.kiji.schema.mapreduce.KijiTableInputFormat
All Implemented Interfaces:
Configurable
public class KijiTableInputFormat
extends InputFormat<EntityId,KijiRowData>
implements Configurable

An InputFormat for MapReduce jobs over Kiji tables. Use the KijiTableInputFormat#setOptions method to configure this input format for use in a mapreduce job.
